<p>
  <strong> As-Salaam-Alaikum, <%= @user.name %></strong>
</p>

<p>
  We hope you are doing well. We wanted to inform you that the <strong><%= @resource.name %></strong> you downloaded from QUL(Quranic
  Universal Library) has a new update.
</p>

<p>
  To ensure you have the most up-to-date version, please visit the link below to download the updated resource:
</p>

<% if @change_log.present? %>
  <div style="margin: 24px 0; padding: 18px; border: 1px dotted #2563eb; background-color: #eff6ff; border-radius: 8px;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1e3a8a;">What's new</h3>
    <strong><%= @change_log.title %></strong>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><%= @change_log.excerpt %></p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
      <%= link_to 'View full change log', change_log_url(@change_log), style: 'color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600;' %>
    </p>
  </div>
<% end %>

<p>
  Please use the link below to download the latest version:
</p>
<p>
  <%= link_to 'Download the Updated Resource', detail_resources_url(@resource.resource_type, @resource.id), class: 'cta-button' %>
</p>
<p>
  We appreciate your involvement in our community, and we are committed to continuously improving the resources we
  provide. If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out.
</p>
